{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2abc9ac2c7","title":"对刘少奇《给普缓同志的信》的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7eb661ffa1","index":0,"year":1947,"month":7,"day":25,"articleId":"2abc9ac2c7"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b7c521cc4","name":"人民战争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b2418d3673","type":"paragraph","text":"对刘少奇《给普缓同志的信》的批语“","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"2abc9ac2c7"},{"id":"fe398f24a2","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年7月25日）少奇同志这封信写得很好，很必要。少奇同志在这封信里所指出的问题，不仅是在一个解放区存在着，而是在一切解放区在不同的程度上存在着：他所指出的原则，则是在一切解放区都适用的因此，应将这封信发到一切地方去，希望各地领导机关将这封信发给党政军各级一切干部，并指示他们研究这封信，用来检查自己领导下的一切群众工作，纠正错误，发扬成绩，彻底解决土地问题，改造一切脱离群众的组织，支持人民战争一直到胜利","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"2abc9ac2c7"},{"id":"62b1eda760","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"2abc9ac2c7"},{"id":"491a96a6b4","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四七年七月二十五日[1]刘少奇发出的《给晋缓同志的信》对晋一些地区群众运动同题作了指示。这是毛泽东对此信的批语。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"2abc9ac2c7"}],"page":{"id":"0dce2dedc5","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"2abc9ac2c7","start":157,"end":157}}}},"__N_SSG":true}